Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Sumire-senpai on for this radio episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:11.08,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me, Tomari!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:16.06,Tomari,,0,0,0,,What's up, Tomari? You've been staring at Sumire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious, Kanon? With this amazing honors student before her very eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,she can't help but fall in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, don't make her say it out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:27.44,Tomari,,0,0,0,,Wrong🤓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:30.58,Kanon,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got it wrong. Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:33.34,Sumire,,0,0,0,,{\i1}*Struggling noises*{\i0} Fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.68,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Then what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:40.40,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Ah, are Natsumi and I gyala-overlapping again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:43.40,Kanon,,0,0,0,,You can just say "overlapping"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:49.86,Tomari,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Sumire and Aneja are similar in their energetic personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.28,Tomari,,0,0,0,,They both enjoy streaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:55.78,Tomari,,0,0,0,,and furthermore, they share in their sensitivity to the latest trends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:00.40,Kanon,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, they do seem close in a lot of areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:06.86,Tomari,,0,0,0,,From my gathering of Sumire-senpai's knowledge, I have come to identify several areas in which she differs from Aneja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.56,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Ara? You've been studying me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:14.54,Sumire,,0,0,0,,So that means... you've become a fan of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:19.54,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Maybe such a cute junior wants an autograph of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:22.54,Tomari,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:24.22,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Guess she's not so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:28.70,Kanon,,0,0,0,,Come on now Sumire, pouting in front of your junior isn't very mature of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:30.92,Sumire,,0,0,0,,I'm not pouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:34.76,Sumire,,0,0,0,,So Tomari, what _did_ you study about me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:41.92,Tomari,,0,0,0,,I learned you had several roles as a child actor, but it seems didn't land you found any as a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:46.50,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Ugh... this girl went right for my weak point...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:52.92,Tomari,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, your failures never stopped you from pursuing the performing arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.00,Sumire,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:59.74,Kanon,,0,0,0,,I didn't really know what you were going through back then either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:03.54,Tomari,,0,0,0,,I felt your approach was very different to my Aneja,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:06.54,Tomari,,0,0,0,,who put herself through various challenges with starry eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:10.78,Tomari,,0,0,0,,This isn't, of course, to appoint one as the better approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.22,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Tomari...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:20.24,Kanon,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Natsumi trying so many different challenges and Sumire's perseverance with getting a lead role are both cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.42,Kanon,,0,0,0,,Cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:25.52,Tomari,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Aneja really is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.34,Tomari,,0,0,0,,You too, Sumire-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:30.30,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Ueh?! Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.62,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Now that you say that, I feel a little embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:38.10,Tomari,,0,0,0,,Aneja is also that way when I compliment her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:43.18,Kanon,,0,0,0,,Hahaha! I can see her saying "You're making me embarrassed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:47.90,Sumire,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright! Enough with the chit-chat, we've gotta start the radio show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:52.16,Kanon,,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan! You're turning red!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.42,Sumire,,0,0,0,,S-s-shut up!!
Comment: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,~~~ END SKIT ~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:13.82,Kanon,,0,0,0,,Everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
